Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.07,0:00:03.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:07.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make \Nsure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:09.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:17.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This here is a secret base for a certain gang \Nof thieves in the west outskirts of Magnolia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:25.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:26.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One-hit knockout!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:29.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so amazing, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:53.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right! I'll yell it out countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:58.70,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe your every tomorrow will be shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:01.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The intersection of all people
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.05,0:01:03.66,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,whose dreams have come true is one point:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:08.29,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Never giving up.  And that's why we're not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:13.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When it seems like you'll be blown away by the headwinds,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:15.62,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,grasp this hand, try to take a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:18.89,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're not alone anymore, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:24.00,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Go forward, more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:26.52,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up on your awesome dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:27.78,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.25,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Move on, my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, with the light shining down upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.71,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about something like giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:36.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you trade being hurt again for strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.14,0:01:41.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes, always looking straight ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:45.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,can surely see the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:03.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are such pushovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:07.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go robbin' people \Nwhen you're such weaklings!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:10.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you'll get away with doing this to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:12.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Devon won't stand for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:14.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We beat that guy a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:16.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finished up over here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:18.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:21.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:26.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you haven't had \Nenough punishment yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:32.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza! Please punish me as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:34.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forced Gate Closure, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That took less time than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:43.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get to go nuts enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:46.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were plenty nuts back there, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:49.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, check out this jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:52.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You can't just go taking that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:54.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Loke over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:56.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a job around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:04.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:08.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect. I wanted to thank you for...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:10.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm in the middle of a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:15.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is {\i1}with{\i0} him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:17.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:19.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He is so totally avoiding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:21.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:46.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Star that Cannot Return to the Heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, shall we go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:58.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, since we actually finished a job early for \Nonce, why don't we head to a spa and take it easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:03:59.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:00.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:07.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:15.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Magnolia's most \Npopular spa town, Hosenka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:22.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Set up by a Duke influenced by the Orient, it \Nis a garish and somewhat iffy tourist spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:28.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, what's with Loke, anyway? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:30.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And a nice bath, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In your armor and all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel more at ease like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:41.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, doesn't it feel kind of gross?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:43.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, yes it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:47.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming to a spa such as this really does \Nmerit complete relaxation, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:50.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet your words are as stiff as ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:54.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're even amazing when you're naked, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:58.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I? Then how about I try \Ngoing around the guild naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:01.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:06.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Upa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:11.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the racket? I'm sleepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:14.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look around you! We're at an inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:17.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nighttime in hotels means pillow fists!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean pillow fights... {lit joke: "pillow punching" vs. "pillow throwing"}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pillows of merit in the \Nroom are already under my control!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Of merit?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will defeat Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:28.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do with you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! Why you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, where'd all these pillows come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:41.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is so happy being of help to Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:50.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, you're next!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:56.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Maybe I'll mix it up myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:13.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I might die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:24.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they even really human?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:29.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Happy's a cat, and you're a dog, Plue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:34.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually a human-pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:35.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:41.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Human... Wait, you can talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:42.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:44.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:49.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am an emissary of the Hero \Nwith the Sacred Stone-pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:53.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes... Stop this \Nfoolishness and come out, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:59.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be stupid enough \Nfor me to fool you for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite a generous guesstimate there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:04.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where are you going, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:08.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Having a pillow fight with those \Nguys is bad for my health.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:11.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey girl, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:14.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That yukata looks great on you. Tourist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:17.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We came here from Oshibana, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:19.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a funky time, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Humor potential overload!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:24.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:27.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Not even a little while, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:31.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're with that cat and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:39.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's okay to take those \Nfunky little fellas with us, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:41.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:42.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're pushy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:45.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:45.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say nya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:50.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, you talk to cats! How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:52.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:53.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:55.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get funky, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:58.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys. That's about...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:01.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? I can't move my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:04.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a good time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:06.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have one funky night, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're wizards?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:09.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:24.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:26.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:30.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:31.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:36.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two have been targeting \Nlone female travelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're criminal wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:41.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the middle of capturing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:47.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to deliver these guys, \Nso if you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:55.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And also for finding my keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:57.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:09:00.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why don't we go out for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a development!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:07.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:12.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating establishment, "Super Express."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:16.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of the top-two most popular \Nspots in the town of Hosenka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:26.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said you'll become hooked on the various \Ndelicacies cooked up by its silent, nodding chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:31.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to stay so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:42.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to ask you this for a while, but \Nwhat did this Celestial Wizard to do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:53.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to tell, I don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:57.74,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Aventure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:57.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not that person, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize if I've hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:08.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:12.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that clichéd breakup line?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:14.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakup, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about breaking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:24.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered something from long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:42.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:44.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to ask, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:48.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:50.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand a bit why you're so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:57.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And for me I thought, we really are friends, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'd better get...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:10.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:14.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...have long to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:42.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:57.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a trick to pick up girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You make them all sad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So? I bet you're pretty surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:14.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I hate jokes like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:19.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Happy, Plue!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:31.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:34.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be swept away by feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:36.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get Lucy involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:51.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They say they got hurt in a pillow \Nfight after their job was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:53.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can people get that \Ninjured in a pillow fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:56.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Gray-sama okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:13:00.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what were you gettin' so worked \Nup about for a pillow fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:02.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give everything 100%!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:04.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:06.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It was you that lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:08.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama won inside Juvia's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy! I'm the one who won, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:14.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:19.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:24.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. There's actually someone other \Nthan Erza who can stop those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:25.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:31.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, you've been in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:34.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I'm totally normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:36.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still angry about me tricking you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:40.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm not that petty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:47.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I just have a lot to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:49.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can always talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is Loke here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:06.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Loke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke's so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:11.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I should ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Loke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're women from the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:19.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they all think \Nthey're Loke's girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:22.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to break up all \Nof a sudden last night! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:24.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say it, but me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:24.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:25.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd he say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:29.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:31.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he finally find "the one?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:32.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it? Is it someone in the guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:37.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:39.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:41.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure she's a little cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's got big boobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:45.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So Loke's true love is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:48.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put me in such a sticky situation, Mira!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:49.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:54.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the sole public bath in Magnolia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:15:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's renowned for regenerating magical \Npower as it relieves fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:04.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Public baths... are Manly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the public bath once \Nin a while sure is nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:13.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing beats soaking in a huge bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:17.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:21.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect after you get out of the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:26.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flavored milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to drink it together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:33.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know I had it pretty rough \Nthis afternoon thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:37.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now... Cheers! To your beautiful eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:41.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:43.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars sure are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:49.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:52.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:57.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happens to \Nshooting stars after they fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:15:59.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:06.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand the sorrow of a star \Nthat cannot return to the heavens?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:14.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's another line to pick up girls, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:16.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can trick me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:19.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:23.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... Everything out of \Nyour mouth is to get girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:27.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I was able to talk \Nwith you casually like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:30.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:44.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Southern Cross, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crux!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So Crux is this old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! His nickname is Crumudgeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:17:00.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of sudden, but I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:05.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you use your power to look into the Celestial \NWizard that Loke was with in the past, Crumudgeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:18.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's asleep, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:20.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, he's looking things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:23.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying! He's totally asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:26.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crumudgeon is a specialist in Celestial Studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:31.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He knows everything about the gates that \Nconnect the Spirit World with the human one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:36.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He knows all about what Celestial Wizards \Ncould call out which spirits in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:40.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:48.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot be too detailed as personal information\Nis protected even in the spirit world, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:54.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the Celestial Wizard connected \Nto Loke is Karen Lilica.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Karen Lilica?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know her, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:03.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a super-famous Celestial Wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:07.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Extremely beautiful, and she used \Nto do photo shoots for Sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:11.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But some years ago she died while on a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:13.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So she was a guild wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:17.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Blue Pegasus, if I recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:22.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So... What was the relationship \Nbetween Loke and Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:26.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry, but that is all I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:27.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:33.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's researching again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:35.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Karen and Loke...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:42.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have long to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:43.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:48.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand the sorrow of a star \Nthat cannot return to the heavens?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:51.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't mean... Loke?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, we have a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:19:00.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke's gone and left Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:02.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:06.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know! Everyone's searching for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:09.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been acting totally weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going to look for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:17.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:19.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:21.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You in there, Loke?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:25.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:28.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:56.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:19:59.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:01.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's searching for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:05.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Karen's grave, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:11.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Celestial Wizard Karen... Your owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:15.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Loke...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:18.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Your real name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:23.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo, the Lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:38.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well to realize I was actually a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:43.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am a Celestial Wizard \Nwith contracts with many spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:45.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally figured out the truth behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:49.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I should have noticed \Nit sooner, shouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:56.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After an incident where the owner dies, \Ntheir contract with the spirit is nullified.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:21:01.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the spirit is forced back to the \Nspirit world until a new owner appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:07.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Karen died, so the contract should be over, \Nand yet you're here in the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:12.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, you can't return \Nto the spirit world, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:19.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as humans can't live in the spirit world, \Nspirits can't live forever in the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:21.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your spirit life-energy will \Nbe slowly drained from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:23.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and finally you will meet your end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:26.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:30.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Three years? I couldn't fathom even one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:33.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at my limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:35.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any strength left at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:38.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to save you somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:43.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why you can't return! \NI'll open the gate for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:45.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:47.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.35,0:21:50.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate you're really going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:52.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I can't go back is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.88,0:21:58.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I broke a fundamental rule \Nbetween owner and spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:03.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of it, I have been banished \Nfrom the spirit world for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:05.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Banished... for eternity?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.91,0:22:08.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:10.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall accept even death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.34,0:22:14.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a spirit, I am a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:16.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My owner was Karen... 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:18.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And with my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.31,0:22:20.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:59.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the spirit world is like?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.36,0:24:03.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, you went through the spirit world \Nonce while grabbing onto Virgo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you see back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.54,0:24:09.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all so sudden. I was \Ngone before I even realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:11.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I might have gotten a \Nglimpse of something, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.30,0:24:12.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.94,0:24:13.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mustache?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.14,0:24:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Spirit King!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.55,0:24:18.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mustache? What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:21.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just have to tune \Nin next time to find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.88,0:24:23.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's a classic preview line!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.99,0:24:26.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
